OL,5, Conservative MP Adam Afriyie has been  
OL,6, made bankrupt after a judge heard he   
OL,7, owed around #1m to HMRC and #700,000 to
OL,8, Barclays bank.                         
OL,10,FA bankruptcy order was made against the
OL,11,FMP at a hearing in the Insolvency and  
OL,12,FCompanies Court on Tuesday.            
OL,14,FThe Windsor MP had already announced he
OL,15,Fwould be standing down at the next     
OL,16,Felection, saying with Brexit           
OL,17,F"concluded" it was the "right time".   
OL,19,FResponding to the court order, Mr      
OL,20,FAfriyie said it was "a stressful time".
